sentences: Andre Lindal (born February 19, 1977) is a Norwegian songwriter, record producer and musician from Oslo, now based in Los Angeles.
After receiving a Grammy nomination for his work with Monica in 2011, he received a Grammy win when Kelly Clarkson's  Stronger took home the Best Pop Vocal Album in 2013.
